title: Grateful Dead Live at Providence Civic Center on 1985-04-04
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Jack Straw, Dire Wolf, El Paso, She Belongs To Me, My Brother Esau, Friend Of The Devil, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Deal

Set 2

I Need A Miracle-> Crazy Fingers, Samson & Delilah, He's Gone-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Drums-> The Wheel-> Black Peter-> Around & Around-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: U.S. Blues

5 star audience recording / 2018 upgrade With no reviews for this recent upgrade / upload, I just had to add a review to let people know that this a not a show or audience recording to pass by.   

Entire show is as on as 85' comes.

The tapers valiant efforts have blessed us with audio bliss.

Enjoy!
